 E[x_0^2] = \int_0^{\infty} \lambda t^2 e^{-\lambda t}  dt = \frac{2}{\lambda^2} 
 E[x_0 x_1] = \int_0^{\infty} \int_0^{\infty} \lambda^2 t_0 t_1 e^{-\lambda t_0} e^{-\lambda t_1 } dt_0 dt_1 = \frac{1}{\lambda^2} 
